.name
ScreenSelect
.author
Markus Aalto 
.version
2.0
.distribution
Freeware
.description
A commodity to change screen order by selecting a screen name from a
listview.  Also allows binding of hotkeys to any screen with a proper name.
Supports automatic activation of windows (remembers last activations) when
changing to new screen, is configurable with Preferences program, has a
full intuition interface and is font sensitive (including proportional
fonts).  Documentation in AmigaGuide, ASCII and DVI formats.  Requires
AmigaOS 2.04 or later.  
